column16: Yasiel Puig walks.   Drew Butera scores.    Dan Haren to 3rd.    Dee Gordon to 2nd.
Dee Gordon walks.   Drew Butera to 3rd.    Dan Haren to 2nd.
Drew Butera doubles (2) on a line drive to left fielder Christian Yelich.
Justin Turner lines out to shortstop Adeiny Hechavarria.
Andre Ethier singles on a line drive to right fielder Giancarlo Stanton.   Matt Kemp scores.
Yonder Alonso flies out to right fielder Giancarlo Stanton.
Chase Headley grounds out, shortstop Adeiny Hechavarria to first baseman Garrett Jones.
